channel.title: Im very mad right now...my server wont let me login
channel.description:
ok i made a server thats whitescape based..i did everything i need to make it work run and compile ext. it said starting sever and its little ip thing..so i go to log in to make sure it works..i log in its working im happy..so i log out to start and edit it and stuff but before i get to my freind logs in im all happy and say i made my own server woot!! stuf like that..i give him my ham and pass and hes on my server no probs..now i cant log in so i ask him to log out so i can get in..still cant log in..so after a while of me trying to find why its doing that my freind had to go so i said ill go to bed its to late..when i get up i try to see if it working...it says to me on the login screen that i have a invaild login request plz switch worlds..and on my bot it says
Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Starting WhiteScape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.72.37.84:3695 eewr: file not found. Did not save for eewr ClientHandler: Client eewr disconnected. ClientHandler: Accepted from 5.72.37.84:3708 eewr: file not found. Did not save for eewr ClientHandler: Client eewr disconnected.
so if anyone can help plz do
